  "text": "Most of the class-D reported in literature does not contain a module allowing the analog volume control for audio, voice and FM [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . In this work we will propose a new architecture of a class-D audio amplifier with analog volume control for high efficiency and low THD.",
